303
00:22:19,126 --> 00:22:21,671
Papa?

304
00:22:21,754 --> 00:22:25,216
Did you see that?

305
00:22:25,299 --> 00:22:28,386
- It's a girl!
- I know it's a girl.

306
00:22:28,469 --> 00:22:31,722
