That's not a request!

356
00:26:44,391 --> 00:26:48,478
Who does she think she is? That girl
has tangled with the wrong man.

357
00:26:48,561 --> 00:26:51,564
- No one says no to Gaston!
- Darn right!

358
00:26:51,648 --> 00:26:55,944
