than I can bear.

360
00:26:57,904 --> 00:27:01,408
- More beer?
- What for? Nothing helps.

361
00:27:01,491 --> 00:27:04,536
- I'm disgraced.
- Who, you? Never!

362
00:27:05,203 --> 00:27:09,040
Gaston, you've got to
pull yourself together.

363
00:27:09,124 --> 00:27:12,252
Gosh, it disturbs me
to see you, Gaston

364
00:27:12,335 --> 00:27:15,296
Looking so
down in the dumps

365
